data.description: Welcome to this charming little ranch style home, perfect for any family! Located in a desirable and well established neighborhood, this house boasts a prime location with parks and playgrounds just a stone's throw away. The property is surrounded by friendly neighbors, creating a warm and welcoming community atmosphere. As you step inside, you'll notice the spacious living room, complete with large windows that allow natural light to pour in, making it a bright and cheerful space. The kitchen is well-equipped and features ample countertop space, ideal for cooking up a storm. The three bedrooms are cozy and inviting, providing a peaceful retreat after a long day. But that's not all - the real showstopper is the expansive backyard! With plenty of greenery and a patio area, it's theperfect spot for family barbecues and outdoor gatherings. The extra room above the garage can be transformed into the ultimate man cave or craft room. This home has everything you need to start building memories with your loved ones. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make it yours today! Features: * Spacious living room with large windows * Well-equipped kitchen * Three cozy bedrooms * Huge backyard with patio area * Extra room above garage (perfect for a man cave or craft room) * Prime location with parks nearby * Friendly neighborhood with great neighbors * Perfect starter home.
